00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:14,519
也就是说
Then...

170
00:09:14,520 --> 00:09:16,800
第四个人站在
a fourth stood...

171
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:20,998
这里  手握杀死这家伙的匕首
here. In their hand, the knife that killed this man

172
00:09:20,999 --> 00:09:22,819
从他身上 我们可以找到
and with him the answer as to why

173
00:09:22,820 --> 00:09:25,798
他在死前打爆这位女士脑袋的原因
he blew this woman's brains out of her before he died.

174
00:09:25,799 --> 00:09:26,906
标记好这些尸体位置
These bodies, mark where

175
00:09:26,907 --> 00:09:28,798
然后把它们送到你的验尸间
they lay and they are for your dead room.

176
00:09:28,799 --> 00:09:31,798
警长 封锁这间房子  真相就在其间
Sergeant, keep this room sealed. There will be truth in it,

177
00:09:31,799 --> 00:09:34,480
但我们必须一点一点地调查 寻求答案
but we must work it inch by every inch to find it.

178
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:40,799
你是警察吗
You're police?

179
00:09:40,800 --> 00:09:43,680
我是伦敦郡议会的Stanley Bone
My name is Stanley Bone of the LCC.

180
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:47,639
我叫Reid  是H警区的
Mine Reid. H Division.

181
00:09:47,640 --> 00:09:49,178
是什么风把我们新郡议会议员
What does it brings a board member

182
00:09:49,179 --> 00:09:51,440
吹到贫民窟清拆这儿来了
of our new county council out to a slum clearance?

183
00:09:51,441 --> 00:09:55,479
您将您的房子提供给这些交房后无处可居之民了吗
Do you offer your home to those here rendered without?

184
00:09:55,480 --> 00:09:58,360
Reid先生 我是制造这场拆迁的
Mr Reid, I am advocate for the railway company

185
00:09:58,361 --> 00:10:00,159
铁路公司的支持者
that makes this incursion.

186
00:10:00,160 --> 00:10:02,798
不管是什么吸引你来此 这事发生在我们的地盘
Whatever has called you here takes place on its land.

187
00:10:02,799 --> 00:10:04,960
我因谋杀案而来
It is murder that calls me here.

188
00:10:04,961 --> 00:10:07,479
谋杀案?  谁被谋杀了
Murder? Of who?

189
00:10:07,480 --> 00:10:09,400
一名收租者和房客
Of a rent collector and tenant.

190
00:10:10,760 --> 00:10:12,919
很遗憾 探长
I am sorry, Inspector.

191
00:10:12,920 --> 00:10:16,079
不过尽管我会为那个死去的可怜人祈祷
But whilst I pray for the poor departed,

192
00:10:16,080 --> 00:10:17,718
这座房子必须今日拆迁
that building comes down today.

193
00:10:17,719 --> 00:10:21,078
不行  在我搞清楚事情始末之前 谁也不准拆
No longer. It stays upright until I know what took place there.

194
00:10:21,079 --> 00:10:23,838
那在你调查租务纠纷之时
And these workmen will stand idle on full wage

195
00:10:23,839 --> 00:10:26,000
我们雇佣的这些全职工人都要一直在此无所事事吗
while you discern the details of a rent dispute?

196
00:10:26,001 --> 00:10:29,960
不论我要调查什么 他们都不准开工
Whatever it is that's discerned here, yes, they will.

197
00:10:31,240 --> 00:10:33,760
或者说您并不支持警察工作?
Or are you not also advocate of the police?

198
00:10:33,761 --> 00:10:35,559
当然支持
Yes, of course.

199
00:10:35,560 --> 00:10:37,440
探长 您可要尽善其责
You must do your duty, Inspector.

200
00:10:42,240 --> 00:10:45,151
现在怎样 探长大人  
How now, Inspector? 

201
00:10:45,152 --> 00:10:47,799
是来看拆迁的进度的吗
Come to see the march of progress, have we?

202
00:10:47,800 --> 00:10:50,718
看看那些寻求栖身之地的人能否如愿?
Those who now must find their shelter where they can?

203
00:10:50,719 --> 00:10:52,339
那是你关心的事   
That your story, is it? 

204
00:10:52,340 --> 00:10:53,960
我可是个有同情心之人
Oh, I am a man of compassion.

205
00:10:53,961 --> 00:10:58,479
愚昧之人要么在这样的地方干活谋生
The benighted souls who must make their lives in such places

206
00:10:58,480 --> 00:11:00,080
要么丧命于此
or meet their deaths there.

207
00:11:02,320 --> 00:11:04,038
透露一两个名字就够了 探长大人
Just a name or two, Inspector, eh?

208
00:11:04,039 --> 00:11:05,912
这边总有人会告诉我的  
Someone here shall tell me eventually. 

209
00:11:05,913 --> 00:11:07,318
为什么你就不能说呢
Why should it not be you?

210
00:11:07,319 --> 00:11:08,879
因为这会给你的生活
Because I would make your life harder 

211
00:11:08,880 --> 00:11:11,480
带来不必要的麻烦 Best先生
than it need be, Mr Best.

212
00:11:11,481 --> 00:11:12,800
而不是更加简单
Not the reverse.

213
00:11:25,920 --> 00:11:28,958
不会有事的 Lucy  会好起来的
It'll be all right, Lucy. It'll be all right.

214
00:11:28,959 --> 00:11:31,558
Artherton 派一辆车到圣乔治十字旗附近去
Artherton, a Maria for St George's Cross.

215
00:11:28,959 --> 00:11:31,558
{\pos(192,26)}圣乔治十字旗:英格兰国旗

216
00:11:31,559 --> 00:11:34,680
令Jackson上校全速返回
Have Captain Jackson return with all... speed.

217
00:11:34,681 --> 00:11:37,480
好了好了  乖  嘘
There, there. Come on. Shush.

218
00:11:38,960 --> 00:11:40,560
你怎么来了
What's brought you here?

219
00:11:40,561 --> 00:11:44,239
我们的Lucy 探长
Erm, our Lucy, Inspector.

220
00:11:44,240 --> 00:11:46,566
Susan女士让我来看看她   
Miss Susan sent me to check on her. 

221
00:11:46,567 --> 00:11:47,600
她的情况如何
And how do you find her?

222
00:11:49,360 --> 00:11:55,279
如您所见 Reid先生  她沉默于痛苦之中
As you see her, Mr Reid. Just... silent in her distress.

223
00:11:55,280 --> 00:11:58,840
- 回家吧 姑娘   - 是 长官
- Get home, girl. - Yes, sir.

224
00:12:01,720 --> 00:12:03,998
那位姑娘的到来似乎让她平静了一些 长官
She seemed calmed by the girl's presence, sir.

225
00:12:03,999 --> 00:12:05,731
- 我以为这有益于她   - 没关系的
- I thought it conducive. - Never mind that,

226
00:12:05,732 --> 00:12:07,166
Artherton  你有没有调查一下她   
Artherton. Have you traced her? 

227
00:12:07,167 --> 00:12:08,200
我没有 长官  这个小伙子调查了
Not myself, sir. The lad.

228
00:12:09,960 --> 00:12:11,000
说吧 Hobbs
Well, Hobbs?

229
00:12:12,160 --> 00:12:15,919
长官 对我来说 那个女孩只是看起来很悲痛
Well, it's only that the girl seems sad, to me, sir.

230
00:12:15,920 --> 00:12:18,276
并不坏   - 不坏   
Not bad. - No. 

231
00:12:18,277 --> 00:12:20,319
如您所说 她曾戴过镣铐
And like you said, she's worn irons before now,

232
00:12:20,320 --> 00:12:22,489
因此我到各个收容所转了转   
so I did a round of the asylums. 

233
00:12:22,490 --> 00:12:23,638
有没有查出什么
And you found knowledge of her?

234
00:12:23,639 --> 00:12:25,918
有的 长官  在贝思纳尔格林的云雀宅
Yes, sir. The Lark House at Bethnal Green.

235
00:12:25,919 --> 00:12:27,344
他们有没有派人来   
And do they send someone? 

236
00:12:27,345 --> 00:12:28,880
来了一位Crabbe医生
A Dr Crabbe comes.

237
00:12:28,881 --> 00:12:31,959
- Karl Crabbe亲自来了?   - 是的长官
- Karl Crabbe himself? - Sir.

238
00:12:31,960 --> 00:12:33,518
他在歇斯底里症研究方面颇有成就
He's made a progress with hysterics

239
00:12:33,519 --> 00:12:35,280
目前这一领域的医生还无人能敌
that no other doctor of the mind has yet.

240
00:12:37,040 --> 00:12:39,078
干得好 Hobbs  你做得对
Good work, Hobbs. You did right.

241
00:12:39,079 --> 00:12:41,172
选两个人 乘警车去找Drake警长吧
Choose two men, take a Maria to Sergeant Drake.

242
00:12:41,173 --> 00:12:42,598
他会指示你该做什么
He'll have instructions for you.

243
00:12:42,599 --> 00:12:44,440
- 遵命 长官   - 把手铐的钥匙给我
- Yes, sir. - Give me the keys to those cuffs.

244
00:12:49,520 --> 00:12:50,680
坐下
Sit.

245
00:13:01,520 --> 00:13:06,000
不  不 孩子  我不是要你来此做这些的
No. No, child. That is not what is... required of you here.

246
00:13:07,800 --> 00:13:09,560
你有没有哪里受伤
Are you wounded in any way?

247
00:13:25,040 --> 00:13:26,919
坐下吧
Sit.

248
00:13:26,920 --> 00:13:30,239
我只希望你开口说话
All I want from you is to talk.

249
00:13:30,240 --> 00:13:31,840
只要您高兴 长官
Whatever pleases you, sir.

250
00:13:34,280 --> 00:13:36,040
喝吧
Drink this.

251
00:13:41,880 --> 00:13:44,960
你还记得是因为什么来到这里吗
Can you remember what it was brought you here?

252
00:13:44,961 --> 00:13:47,359
在狗脖儿胡同发生了什么
What happened at the Dog's Neck?

253
00:13:47,360 --> 00:13:49,319
我的妈妈被杀了 长官
My mama killed, sir.

254
00:13:49,320 --> 00:13:50,560
不仅仅是你的妈妈吧
Not just your mother.

255
00:13:51,680 --> 00:13:53,279
还有一个男人
A man, too.

256
00:13:53,280 --> 00:13:55,120
没错  你认识他吗
Yes. Do you know him?

257
00:13:57,280 --> 00:13:58,520
你看到了什么
What did you see?

258
00:14:01,360 --> 00:14:03,523
恕我冒昧 Eames小姐  
Forgive me, Miss Eames. 

259
00:14:03,524 --> 00:14:04,760
他的血溅了你一身
His blood was shed all upon you.

260
00:14:06,840 --> 00:14:08,360
长官 我可以离开了吗
May I go now, sir?

261
00:14:12,640 --> 00:14:15,600
Lucy 你以为你现在在哪里
Where is it that you think you are, Lucy?

262
00:14:21,240 --> 00:14:22,560
我忘了
I forget.

263
00:14:27,640 --> 00:14:30,120
你的妈妈 还有这个男人...
Your mama, this man...

264
00:14:31,200 --> 00:14:34,599
帮我 也是帮你自己 好好想想
Help me, help you and think.

265
00:14:34,600 --> 00:14:35,640
你看到了什么
What did you see?

266
00:14:37,120 --> 00:14:38,520
我只看到了我的黑暗
Just my darkness.

267
00:14:40,560 --> 00:14:43,760
当我醒来 他们就躺在我面前
When I woke up, they were there laid before me.

268
00:14:43,761 --> 00:14:45,520
没有其他人?   
And not another soul? 

269
00:14:45,521 --> 00:14:47,600
没有   - 你确定?
No-one. - You are sure?

270
00:14:50,120 --> 00:14:52,800
长官 这世上没有我确定之事
There's nothing that I'm sure of in this world, sir.

271
00:14:54,520 --> 00:14:58,120
Lucy 你知道你怀孕了吗
Lucy, you are aware that you are with child, are you not?

272
00:15:11,560 --> 00:15:13,400
Crabbe医生
Dr Crabbe.

273
00:15:15,920 --> 00:15:17,760
Lucy
Lucy!

274
00:15:20,960 --> 00:15:22,319
Reid先生
Mr Reid.

275
00:15:22,320 --> 00:15:23,679
医生
Sir.

276
00:15:23,680 --> 00:15:25,838
我上个月听了您的演讲  在林肯律师学院
I heard you speak last month. At Lincoln's Inn.

277
00:15:25,839 --> 00:15:27,806
在学院的那次  我认识的一个人跟我说
At the college! A man I know told me 

278
00:15:27,807 --> 00:15:29,118
那天我语调低沉 内容单调
I droned that day.

279
00:15:29,119 --> 00:15:30,720
那他一定没有认真听
He cannot have been listening.

280
00:15:30,721 --> 00:15:34,119
现在你找到了我们的Lucy 并照顾她
And now you have found and cared for our Lucy.

281
00:15:34,120 --> 00:15:36,039
Crabbe医生 我想告诉您
Dr Crabbe, you should know,

282
00:15:36,040 --> 00:15:38,240
Eames小姐的妈妈今天被杀害了
Miss Eames' mother is killed this day.

283
00:15:41,480 --> 00:15:43,679
哦 我可怜的孩子
Oh, my poor dear girl.

284
00:15:43,680 --> 00:15:44,898
被杀害的还有另一个人 
And another man, too, 

285
00:15:44,899 --> 00:15:46,560
名为Roach  您认识他吗?
the name of Roach. Do you know him, sir?

286
00:15:46,561 --> 00:15:48,879
不 我不认识  Lucy怀孕了?
No, I do not. Was Lucy present?

287
00:15:48,880 --> 00:15:50,039
是的
She was.

288
00:15:50,040 --> 00:15:51,560
但是什么都不记得了?
But remembers not a thing?

289
00:15:53,320 --> 00:15:55,638
把这些尸体送到我的验尸房去
Get both these bodies to my dead room!

290
00:15:55,639 --> 00:15:58,720
谁出了差错就去协助我验尸
The man who drops them will be assisting me at autopsy.

291
00:16:00,120 --> 00:16:01,600
不要  等等  等等
No! Wait! Wait!

292
00:16:02,720 --> 00:16:05,160
快抬走  快  迅速点
Take them away now! Hurry! Hurry!

293
00:16:22,120 --> 00:16:23,760
Reid 很 很抱歉
Reid, I... I'm sorry.

294
00:16:27,840 --> 00:16:29,359
她患有癫痫?
She is epileptic?

295
00:16:29,360 --> 00:16:33,319
她受癫痫折磨 没错  还有其他病症
She is ailed by that, yes. Other conditions, also.

296
00:16:33,320 --> 00:16:36,358
探长 我知道你还想继续审问她
Inspector, I know you must question her further

297
00:16:36,359 --> 00:16:39,360
但你再次需要她之前 我要先带回去照顾她
but I would lodge her in my care until you next have need of her.

298
00:16:41,600 --> 00:16:42,998
Artherton 准备文件
Artherton, prepare the papers.

299
00:16:42,999 --> 00:16:44,400
Davis 帮我抱起她
Davis, can we lift her?

300
00:16:44,401 --> 00:16:46,519
谢谢
Thank you.

301
00:16:46,520 --> 00:16:50,760
好了 Lucy  没事了 没事了
There Lucy. All is well, all is well.

302
00:16:56,160 --> 00:16:58,598
Crabbe医生 在您离开之前我想再问一句
Dr Crabbe, one last question before you go.

303
00:16:58,599 --> 00:17:00,798
Eames小姐做您的病人已经多久了?
For how long has Miss Eames been a patient of yours?

304
00:17:00,799 --> 00:17:02,598
两年多一点
A little over two years now,

305
00:17:02,599 --> 00:17:05,118
不过她不是一直跟我住在一起
but she is not permanently resident with me.

306
00:17:05,119 --> 00:17:06,718
您没有一直照管着她吗
You keep no watch over her?

307
00:17:06,719 --> 00:17:08,234
探长 要想治好她的病 
Inspector, to find her health, 

308
00:17:08,235 --> 00:17:10,438
让她感觉自己像你我一样
it is of considerable importance

309
00:17:10,439 --> 00:17:13,998
正常地生活无比重要
that Lucy's life feel as commonplace as yours or mine.

310
00:17:13,999 --> 00:17:16,239
如果让她觉得我们在评判她的一举一动 
That cannot be the case 

311
00:17:16,240 --> 00:17:17,360
那恢复健康便是无望
if she feel we assess her every move.

312
00:17:17,361 --> 00:17:20,239
她不舒服的时候 就去找我
When she is ill, she comes to me.

313
00:17:20,240 --> 00:17:23,160
没事的时候 就爱怎么生活就怎么生活
When well, she lives as she pleases.

314
00:17:28,400 --> 00:17:29,680
不好意思
Excuse me.

315
00:17:35,480 --> 00:17:37,399
长官  这些小家伙们
Sir. These nippers?

316
00:17:37,400 --> 00:17:39,118
我知道一个地方可以收养他们
I have an idea where they may rest

317
00:17:39,119 --> 00:17:41,600
在他们得到更好的归宿之前
until we know better what will become of them.

318
00:17:55,120 --> 00:17:57,574
Goren小姐  Goren小姐 很抱歉
Miss Goren? Miss Goren, I am sorry.

319
00:17:57,575 --> 00:17:59,959
我又来麻烦您了
I come to impose on you once more.

320
00:17:59,960 --> 00:18:02,959
哦  朋友之间不必见外 探长
Oh! We are friends now, Inspector.

321
00:18:02,960 --> 00:18:05,000
想来就来 完全不必道歉
You must never apologise for your visit.

322
00:18:05,001 --> 00:18:06,519
这位小姑娘是Betsy
This is Betsy.

323
00:18:06,520 --> 00:18:07,680
你好啊 Betsy
Hello, Betsy!

324
00:18:09,320 --> 00:18:11,360
孩子们 快来欢迎小妹妹Betsy
Girls, say hello to Betsy.

325
00:18:13,600 --> 00:18:15,758
这个可怜的孩子经历了怎样的故事
What is this poor child's story?

326
00:18:15,759 --> 00:18:18,278
她的妈妈死了 她姐姐...
Er, her mother is dead and her sister...

327
00:18:18,279 --> 00:18:20,720
她姐姐暂时照顾不了她
Her sister is of no use to her for now.

328
00:18:20,721 --> 00:18:22,359
没有爸爸或叔叔什么的吗
No father or uncle?

329
00:18:22,360 --> 00:18:24,638
这个家庭就是被男人毁掉的 Goren小姐
It's men that are the ruin of this family, Miss Goren.

330
00:18:24,639 --> 00:18:27,320
不仅仅是这个家庭 好多都是如此 探长
Oh, this family and many like them, Inspector.

331
00:18:28,600 --> 00:18:30,079
你不这么认为吗
You disagree?

332
00:18:30,080 --> 00:18:33,640
哦 不 不是的 只是 我妻子也会这样说 
No, no. No, merely, my wife would say the same.

333
00:18:36,080 --> 00:18:38,861
Reid夫人一定是一位理智聪慧 
Mrs Reid must be a woman 

334
00:18:38,862 --> 00:18:40,079
心智明晰的女人
of great sense and clarity.

335
00:18:40,080 --> 00:18:41,999
没错 她是
She is that, yes.



336
00:18:42,000 --> 00:18:43,800
那我希望与她一见
Then I would like to meet her.

337
00:18:48,520 --> 00:18:50,480
再次多谢 Goren小姐
My many thanks again, Miss Goren.

338
00:18:52,760 --> 00:18:55,000
如果有什么消息 我会首先通知你
If I have news, you'll be the first to know.

339
00:19:13,320 --> 00:19:15,839
你还记得你的屋子吗 Lucy
You remember, Lucy? Your room?

340
00:19:15,840 --> 00:19:18,040
一切都没变
Just as it ever was.

341
00:19:43,760 --> 00:19:46,318
奇怪 就好像她从不曾在这里过
Strange, were like she weren't even there.

342
