So what then? Are they Lucy's?

367
00:20:59,120 --> 00:21:01,598
长官 警监Munro让您过去
Commissioner Munro calls for you, Sir.

368
00:21:01,599 --> 00:21:04,320
他要你陪他去一趟狗脖儿胡同的铁路挖掘现场
You're to go with him to the Dog's Neck railway excavation.

369
00:21:17,600 --> 00:21:19,238
那里才开发了几周
They are but a few weeks old,

370
00:21:19,239 --> 00:21:22,280
但已经带来了亘古不散的寒意
but these places already have the chill of eternity.

371
00:21:23,680 --> 00:21:25,399
长官 你为什么叫我来
Why bring me here, Sir?

372
00:21:25,400 --> 00:21:28,194
Reid 只想让你亲自听听这个人的话 
Just hear the man out, Reid. 

373
00:21:28,195 --> 00:21:29,960
他的意见是我们不该忽视的
His concern should be ours, also.

374
00:21:35,280 --> 00:21:36,960
探长 探长 请这边来
Inspector. Inspector, please!

375
00:21:39,160 --> 00:21:42,438
谢谢你迅速赶到
Thank you for responding so speedily to my invitation.

376
00:21:42,439 --> 00:21:44,238
我很欣慰 特别是对你 探长
Yourself in particular, Inspector.

377
00:21:44,239 --> 00:21:46,998
有话直说 Bone 我那里还有两个谋杀案等着呢
Get to it, Bone, I have two murders above us need investigation.

378
00:21:46,999 --> 00:21:50,198
我一定会速战速决 不多叨扰 Reid先生
And I will have you returned to them in short order, Mr Reid.

379
00:21:50,199 --> 00:21:52,678
等你看过这里到底在修建什么之后
As soon as you've seen just what is built here.

380
00:21:52,679 --> 00:21:55,480
铺设铁路而已 多新鲜啊
Track is laid. For a railway. It is nothing new.

381
00:21:55,481 --> 00:21:58,719
或许不新鲜  但绝对有新意
Perhaps not new. But newly efficient.

382
00:21:58,720 --> 00:22:01,280
