Onwards, for ever.

387
00:22:28,989 --> 00:22:32,158
延伸过下一个世纪 再下一个
Down the next century and the one that follows -

388
00:22:32,159 --> 00:22:33,678
组成一张有机的运输网
an organism of transport.

389
00:22:33,679 --> 00:22:35,958
每一个区都彼此相连
Every borough connected, one to the other.

390
00:22:35,959 --> 00:22:38,558
旅行不再仅仅是富人的特权 
The poor, sir - not simply the rich - will travel,

391
00:22:38,559 --> 00:22:40,307
因为旅费会大幅下降
for the cost of half a pot of jam,

392
00:22:40,308 --> 00:22:42,158
从城市的一边到另一边花费无几
from one end of our city to another.

393
00:22:42,159 --> 00:22:44,118
随着每天他们的视野的开拓
Their everyday horizon extended,

394
00:22:44,119 --> 00:22:46,798
他们的志向也会相应提高
their aspirations improved accordingly.

395
00:22:46,799 --> 00:22:48,329
Bone先生 我从未质疑过
Mr Bone, I have never contested

396
00:22:48,330 --> 00:22:50,600
这项工程对人们的生活的意义
the value of this machinery to people's lives.

397
00:22:50,601 --> 00:22:51,799
那就促进它吧
Then assist it.

398
00:22:51,800 --> 00:22:55,598
探长 我们为这个事业所投入的资金网
Inspector, the investment structure we have constructed for this

399
00:22:55,599 --> 00:22:57,497
犹如我们即将建造的铁路网 
venture, it is as reticulated 

400
00:22:57,498 --> 00:22:58,958
都层层相套 环环相扣
as the network we would build.

401
00:22:58,959 --> 00:23:01,398
每一个环节都有一个完工保障
Each section of line has a completion guarantee.

402
00:23:01,399 --> 00:23:02,583
只有保证这个环节完成
That guarantee fulfilled,

403
00:23:02,584 --> 00:23:04,478
下一部分的建筑资金才会发放
the next tranche of capital is released.

404
00:23:04,479 --> 00:23:06,920
如果地面上的拆迁人员继续无所事事
Should the demolition crew above ground stand idle

405
00:23:06,921 --> 00:23:11,559
我们这里整个工程就会有毁于一旦的危险
for many hours more, we risk the collapse of the entire venture.

406
00:23:11,560 --> 00:23:13,800
所以我拜托你 先生 求求你了
I beg you, sir. I beg you.

407
00:23:15,000 --> 00:23:16,520
让他们继续开工吧
Let them proceed.

408
00:23:19,880 --> 00:23:21,518
日安 先生们
Good day to you, fine sirs.

409
00:23:21,519 --> 00:23:22,678
这位是谁啊
Who is this gentleman?

410
00:23:22,679 --> 00:23:25,078
他叫Best 他是星报的撰稿记者
His name is Best. He writes for The Star.

411
00:23:25,079 --> 00:23:27,718
议员先生 您并不认得我 但我今天是来结交您的
You know me not, Councillor. But I come to know you, Sir.

412
00:23:27,719 --> 00:23:29,078
这里是私人产业
This is private land.

413
00:23:29,079 --> 00:23:32,118
马上滚蛋 否则Reid探长会用靴底送你一程
Remove yourself or Inspector Reid shall do so with his boot.

414
00:23:32,119 --> 00:23:33,440
可此刻我站在一块公共区域上
And this here is common land

415
00:23:33,441 --> 00:23:35,518
在此我想提问Bone先生几个问题
from which I shall ask Mr Bone my questions,

416
00:23:35,519 --> 00:23:38,160
就是他是如何评价 在他投身郡议会的
of how he feels, four months into its life,

417
00:23:38,161 --> 00:23:40,399
四个月里 议会的作为呢
our new county council proceeds.

418
00:23:40,400 --> 00:23:44,919
如果议会启蒙公民的职能 还没有被议员们
If its civic enlightenments are not compromised by the...

419
00:23:44,920 --> 00:23:48,079
追逐铜臭的商业心所瓦解的话
commercial instincts of its councillors.

420
00:23:48,080 --> 00:23:51,198
我不想在这接着听你含沙射影了
I shall not stand here and listen to these insinuations.

421
00:23:51,199 --> 00:23:53,358
我们所做的一切都是为了整个城市
Everything we do, we do for the good of this city

422
00:23:53,359 --> 00:23:55,960
为了城市里百姓大众们的利益
and the benefit of those who build their lives within it.

423
00:23:55,961 --> 00:23:58,279
警监 探员 我先失陪了
Commissioner, Inspector.

424
