Best 你说够了没  快滚
Best! Enough. Get gone.

434
00:24:26,120 --> 00:24:28,359
悉听尊便 探长
Whatever you say, Inspector.

435
00:24:28,360 --> 00:24:30,120
但我还会回来的
But do not think me gone long.

436
00:24:35,320 --> 00:24:37,126
就我个人来说 Bone先生对未来的规划
For myself, Mr Bone's vision

437
00:24:37,127 --> 00:24:40,160
就是交通密集型城市的构想 我不置可否
of a liberal city commune is of little bearing.

438
00:24:40,161 --> 00:24:41,399
是的 长官
No, sir.

439
00:24:41,400 --> 00:24:43,678
对我而言重要的是
What is of greater importance to me is this 

440
00:24:43,679 --> 00:24:46,238
一旦一个既成的平民窟
that each occasion a slum is raised to the ground,

441
00:24:46,239 --> 00:24:50,078
被整洁的钢筋水泥所取代
it is replaced by the type of brick and clean steel on which

442
00:24:50,079 --> 00:24:53,998
