the bacteria of the criminal classes can no longer fester.

443
00:24:53,999 --> 00:24:57,440
要是我们能把大量游民送到外面的广阔世界
The greater the number of homeless we send to the wider world,

444
00:24:57,441 --> 00:25:00,319
我们的犯罪率就会显著下降
the faster our measure of crime falls.

445
00:25:00,320 --> 00:25:02,118
我就是这个意思 探长
You have my meaning, inspector.

446
00:25:02,119 --> 00:25:04,499
不管你的人在贫民窟里有什么要事
Whatever it is your men do in that rookery,

447
00:25:04,500 --> 00:25:05,718
